        <h2>About AUCA Certificate Generator</h2>
        <p>The **Adventist University of Central Africa (AUCA)** is committed to academic excellence and integrity. This digital certificate system was developed to streamline the issuance and verification of **Certificates of Good Standing**.</p>
        
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>To provide a secure, efficient, and professional platform for students and administrators to manage academic documentation with ease and transparency.</p>
        
        <h3>Key Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Digital Verification:</strong> Every certificate includes a unique QR code for instant authenticity checks.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Integrity:</strong> Direct integration with official university records.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainable:</strong> Reduces paper waste by enabling digital sharing and verification.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For more information about our academic programs, please visit the official <a href="http://www.auca.ac.rw" target="_blank">AUCA Website</a>.</p>
    </div>
